<li id="cite_note-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://catholicoutlook.org/toongabbies-thomist-philosopher-parra/">"Toongabbie's Thomist philosopher"</a>. <i>Catholic Outlook</i>. 2018-07-16<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2022-10-02</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Catholic+Outlook&amp;rft.atitle=Toongabbie%27s+Thomist+philosopher&amp;rft.date=2018-07-16&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fcatholicoutlook.org%2Ftoongabbies-thomist-philosopher-parra%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANeo-scholasticism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
